[2026-03-31 03:03:12] [DEBUG] [PPT PostToolUse Hook] stdin 数据: {"session_id":"31a4c6a8-fd14-4c06-b277-812f5bda5c54","transcript_path":"/root/.codebuddy/projects/workspace/31a4c6a8-fd14-4c06-b277-812f5bda5c54.jsonl","cwd":"/workspace","hook_event_name":"PostToolUse","tool_name":"Write","tool_input":{"file_path":"/root/.codebuddy/plans/blazing-forging-turing.md","content":"# NovaFrame PHP 框架插件系统设计方案\n\n## 一、框架现状分析总结\n\n### 1.1 核心架构特点\n\n| 组件 | 实现方式 | 关键文件 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| 容器 | Symfony DI Container + 自定义封装 | `/workspace/framework/Container/Container.php` |\n| 路由 | Symfony Routing + PHP 8 Attributes | `/workspace/framework/Core/AttributeRouteLoader.php` |\n| 控制器 | BaseController + 自动依赖注入 | `/workspace/framework/Basic/BaseController.php` |\n| 服务提供者 | ServiceProviderInterface | `/workspace/framework/Container/ServiceProviderInterface.php` |\n| 启动流程 | Container::init() -> Kernel::boot() -> Framework::loadAllRoutes() | `/workspace/framework/Core/Framework.php` |\n\n### 1.2 现有硬编码问题\n\n```php\n// Framework.php 中的硬编码\nprivate const CONTROLLER_DIR = BASE_PATH . '/app/Controllers';\nprivate const CONTROLLER_NAMESPACE = 'App\\Controllers';\n\n// AttributeRouteLoader.php 构造函数\npublic function __construct(string $controller_dir, string $controller_namespace, ...)\n\n// Router.php 中的命名空间\nprivate const DEFAULT_CONTROLLER_NAMESPACE = 'App\\Controllers';\n```\n\n### 1.3 服务提供者机制\n\n框架已实现完整的 ServiceProvider 模式：\n- `ServiceProviderInterface`: 定义 `register()` 和 `boot()` 两个生命周期方法\n- `ContainerProviders`: 自动扫描目录加载 Provider\n- 支持 `Framework\\Providers\\` 和 `App\\Providers\\` 双命名空间\n\n---\n\n## 二、插件系统设计方案\n\n### 2.1 目录结构设计\n\n```\n/workspace\n├── app/                          # 主应用目录\n│   ├── Controllers/\n│   ├── Services/\n│   ├── Models/\n│   ├── Middlewares/\n│   └── Providers/\n│\n├── plugins/                      # 插件根目录（新增）\n│   ├── Blog/                     # 插件示例：Blog 插件\n│   │   ├── plugin.json           # 插件元数据配置\n│   │   ├── Controllers/          # 插件控制器\n│   │   │   └── PostController.php\n│   │   ├── Services/             # 插件服务\n│   │   │   └── PostService.php\n│   │   ├── Models/               # 插件模型\n│   │   │   └── Post.php\n│   │   ├── Middlewares/          # 插件中间件\n│   │   │   └── PostAuthMiddleware.php\n│   │   ├── Providers/            # 插件服务提供者\n│   │   │   └── BlogServiceProvider.php\n│   │   ├── database/             # 数据库迁移\n│   │   │   ├── migrations/\n│   │   │   │   └── 20240101_create_posts_table.php\n│   │   │   └── seeds/\n│   │   │       └── PostSeeder.php\n│   │   ├── views/                # 插件视图模板\n│   │   │   └── post/\n│   │   │       └── list.html.twig\n│   │   ├── routes.php            # 插件路由配置（可选）\n│   │   └── config.php            # 插件配置文件\n│   │\n│   └── Payment/                  # 插件示例：支付插件\n│       ├── plugin.json\n│       ├── Controllers/\n│       ├── Services/\n│       └── ...\n│\n├── config/\n│   ├── plugin/                   # 插件配置目录（新增）\n│   │   ├── plugins.php           # 已安装插件清单\n│   │   ├── blog.php              # Blog 插件运行时配置\n│   │   └── payment.php           # Payment 插件运行时配置\n│   └── ...\n│\n├── storage/\n│   └── plugins/                  # 插件数据存储（新增）\n│       ├── cache/                # 插件缓存\n│       └── logs/                 # 插件日志\n│\n└── framework/\n    ├── Plugin/                   # 插件系统核心（新增）\n    │   ├── PluginManager.php     # 插件管理器\n    │   ├── PluginInterface.php   # 插件接口\n    │   ├── PluginManifest.php    # 插件清单解析器\n    │   ├── PluginLoader.php      # 插件加载器\n    │   ├── PluginRepository.php  # 插件仓库（数据库操作）\n    │   ├── Exceptions/           # 插件异常\n    │   │   └── PluginException.php\n    │   └── Console/              # 插件命令行工具\n    │       ├── PluginInstallCommand.php\n    │       ├── PluginUninstallCommand.php\n    │       ├── PluginEnableCommand.php\n    │       └── PluginListCommand.php\n    └── ...\n```\n\n### 2.2 插件配置规范\n\n#### 2.2.1 plugin.json（插件元数据）\n\n```json\n{\n    \"name\": \"nova/blog\",\n    \"title\": \"博客管理插件\",\n    \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n    \"description\": \"提供文章管理、分类管理、标签管理等功能\",\n    \"type\": \"plugin\",\n    \"namespace\": \"Plugin\\\\Blog\",\n    \"author\": {\n        \"name\": \"NovaFrame Team\",\n        \"email\": \"team@novaframe.com\"\n    },\n    \"homepage\": \"https://github.com/novaframe/blog-plugin\",\n    \"license\": \"MIT\",\n    \"require\": {\n        \"php\": \"^8.1\",\n        \"novaframe/framework\": \"^2.0\"\n    },\n    \"require_plugins\": {\n        \"nova/user\": \"^1.0\"\n    },\n    \"autoload\": {\n        \"psr-4\": {\n            \"Plugin\\\\Blog\\\\\": \"\"\n        }\n    },\n    \"providers\": [\n        \"Plugin\\\\Blog\\\\Providers\\\\BlogServiceProvider\"\n    ],\n    \"routes\": {\n        \"prefix\": \"/blog\",\n        \"middleware\": [\"auth\"]\n    },\n    \"migrations\": true,\n    \"seeds\": true,\n    \"hooks\": {\n        \"install\": \"Plugin\\\\Blog\\\\Install::run\",\n        \"uninstall\": \"Plugin\\\\Blog\\\\Install::uninstall\",\n        \"enable\": \"Plugin\\\\Blog\\\\Install::enable\",\n        \"disable\": \"Plugin\\\\Blog\\\\Install::disable\",\n        \"upgrade\": \"Plugin\\\\Blog\\\\Install::upgrade\"\n    },\n    \"config\": {\n        \"posts_per_page\": 10,\n        \"enable_comments\": true,\n        \"moderate_comments\": true\n    },\n    \"permissions\": [\n        \"blog.post.view\",\n        \"blog.post.create\",\n        \"blog.post.edit\",\n        \"blog.post.delete\"\n    ]\n}\n```\n\n#### 2.2.2 config/plugin/plugins.php（已安装插件清单）\n\n```php\n<?php\nreturn [\n    // 已安装插件列表\n    'installed' => [\n        'nova/blog' => [\n            'version' => '1.0.0',\n            'enabled' => true,\n            'installed_at' => '2024-01-15 10:30:00',\n            'updated_at' => '2024-01-15 10:30:00',\n        ],\n        'nova/payment' => [\n            'version' => '2.1.0',\n            'enabled' => false,\n            'installed_at' => '2024-01-10 09:00:00',\n            'updated_at' => '2024-01-12 14:30:00',\n        ],\n    ],\n    \n    // 插件依赖关系图（自动生成）\n    'dependencies' => [\n        'nova/blog' => ['nova/user'],\n    ],\n    \n    // 插件加载顺序（自动生成）\n    'load_order' => [\n        'nova/user',\n        'nova/blog',\n        'nova/payment',\n    ],\n];\n```\n\n#### 2.2.3 插件独立配置文件 config/plugin/blog.php\n\n```php\n<?php\nreturn [\n    // 插件运行时配置（可被用户覆盖）\n    'posts_per_page' => env('BLOG_POSTS_PER_PAGE', 10),\n    'enable_comments' => env('BLOG_ENABLE_COMMENTS', true),\n    'moderate_comments' => env('BLOG_MODERATE_COMMENTS', true),\n    \n    // 插件特有的配置\n    'seo' => [\n        'meta_title_suffix' => ' | My Blog',\n        'generate_sitemap' => true,\n    ],\n];\n```\n\n### 2.3 核心接口设计\n\n#### 2.3.1 PluginInterface.php\n\n```php\n<?php\nnamespace Framework\\Plugin;\n\ninterface PluginInterface\n{\n    /**\n     * 获取插件名称\n     */\n    public function getName(): string;\n    \n    /**\n     * 获取插件版本\n     */\n    public function getVersion(): string;\n    \n    /**\n     * 插件安装时调用\n     */\n    public function install(): void;\n    \n    /**\n     * 插件卸载时调用\n     */\n    public function uninstall(): void;\n    \n    /**\n     * 插件启用时调用\n     */\n    public function enable(): void;\n    \n    /**\n     * 插件禁用时调用\n     */\n    public function disable(): void;\n    \n    /**\n     * 插件升级时调用\n     */\n    public function upgrade(string $oldVersion, string $newVersion): void;\n}\n```\n\n#### 2.3.2 PluginManifest.php（插件清单解析器）\n\n```php\n<?php\nnamespace Framework\\Plugin;\n\nclass PluginManifest\n{\n    protected array $manifest = [];\n    protected string $path;\n    \n    public function __construct(string $pluginPath)\n    {\n        $this->path = $pluginPath;\n        $this->load();\n    }\n    \n    protected function load(): void\n    {\n        $file = $this->path . '/plugin.json';\n        if (!file_exists($file)) {\n            throw new PluginException(\"Plugin manifest not found: {$file}\");\n        }\n        \n        $content = file_get_contents($file);\n        $this->manifest = json_decode($content, true);\n        \n        if (json_last_error() !== JSON_ERROR_NONE) {\n            throw new PluginException(\"Invalid plugin.json: \" . json_last_error_msg());\n        }\n        \n        $this->validate();\n    }\n    \n    protected function validate(): void\n    {\n        $required = ['name', 'version', 'namespace'];\n        foreach ($required as $field) {\n            if (empty($this->manifest[$field])) {\n                throw new PluginException(\"Missing required field: {$field}\");\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 验证版本格式\n        if (!preg_match('/^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+(-[\\w\\.]+)?$/', $this->manifest['version'])) {\n            throw new PluginException(\"Invalid version format\");\n        }\n    }\n    \n    public function getName(): string\n    {\n        return $this->manifest['name'];\n    }\n    \n    public function getVersion(): string\n    {\n        return $this->manifest['version'];\n    }\n    \n    public function getNamespace(): string\n    {\n        return rtrim($this->manifest['namespace'], '\\\\');\n    }\n    \n    public function getProviders(): array\n    {\n        return $this->manifest['providers'] ?? [];\n    }\n    \n    public function getRouteConfig(): array\n    {\n        return $this->manifest['routes'] ?? [];\n    }\n    \n    public function getDependencies(): array\n    {\n        return $this->manifest['require_plugins'] ?? [];\n    }\n    \n    public function getHooks(): array\n    {\n        return $this->manifest['hooks'] ?? [];\n    }\n    \n    public function getConfig(): array\n    {\n        return $this->manifest['config'] ?? [];\n    }\n    \n    public function all(): array\n    {\n        return $this->manifest;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 2.4 插件管理器核心实现\n\n#### 2.4.1 PluginManager.php\n\n```php\n<?php\nnamespace Framework\\Plugin;\n\nuse Framework\\Container\\Container;\nuse Framework\\Core\\AttributeRouteLoader;\nuse Psr\\Log\\LoggerInterface;\nuse Symfony\\Component\\Routing\\RouteCollection;\n\nclass PluginManager\n{\n    protected Container $container;\n    protected LoggerInterface $logger;\n    protected array $plugins = [];\n    protected array $enabledPlugins = [];\n    protected array $config;\n    \n    public function __construct(Container $container, LoggerInterface $logger)\n    {\n        $this->container = $container;\n        $this->logger = $logger;\n        $this->config = $this->loadConfig();\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 加载插件配置\n     */\n    protected function loadConfig(): array\n    {\n        $file = BASE_PATH . '/config/plugin/plugins.php';\n        if (file_exists($file)) {\n            return require $file;\n        }\n        return ['installed' => [], 'dependencies' => [], 'load_order' => []];\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 发现所有已安装插件\n     */\n    public function discover(): array\n    {\n        $pluginDir = BASE_PATH . '/plugins';\n        if (!is_dir($pluginDir)) {\n            return [];\n        }\n        \n        $discovered = [];\n        $dirs = scandir($pluginDir);\n        \n        foreach ($dirs as $dir) {\n            if ($dir === '.' || $dir === '..') {\n                continue;\n            }\n            \n            $path = $pluginDir . '/' . $dir;\n            if (!is_dir($path)) {\n                continue;\n            }\n            \n            try {\n                $manifest = new PluginManifest($path);\n                $discovered[$manifest->getName()] = [\n                    'manifest' => $manifest,\n                    'path' => $path,\n                    'status' => $this->getPluginStatus($manifest->getName()),\n                ];\n            } catch (PluginException $e) {\n                $this->logger->warning(\"Invalid plugin: {$dir} - \" . $e->getMessage());\n            }\n        }\n        \n        $this->plugins = $discovered;\n        return $discovered;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 获取插件状态\n     */\n    protected function getPluginStatus(string $name): array\n    {\n        return $this->config['installed'][$name] ?? ['enabled' => false];\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 加载所有启用的插件\n     */\n    public function loadEnabled(): void\n    {\n        // 按依赖顺序加载\n        $loadOrder = $this->resolveLoadOrder();\n        \n        foreach ($loadOrder as $pluginName) {\n            if (!isset($this->plugins[$pluginName])) {\n                continue;\n            }\n            \n            $plugin = $this->plugins[$pluginName];\n            \n            if (!$plugin['status']['enabled']) {\n                continue;\n            }\n            \n            $this->loadPlugin($plugin);\n        }\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 解析插件加载顺序（拓扑排序）\n     */\n    protected function resolveLoadOrder(): array\n    {\n        if (!empty($this->config['load_order'])) {\n            return $this->config['load_order'];\n        }\n        \n        // 拓扑排序算法\n        $graph = [];\n        $inDegree = [];\n        \n        foreach ($this->plugins as $name => $plugin) {\n            $inDegree[$name] = 0;\n            $graph[$name] = [];\n        }\n        \n        // 构建依赖图\n        foreach ($this->plugins as $name => $plugin) {\n            $deps = $plugin['manifest']->getDependencies();\n            foreach ($deps as $dep => $version) {\n                if (isset($this->plugins[$dep])) {\n                    $graph[$dep][] = $name;\n                    $inDegree[$name]++;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // Kahn 算法\n        $queue = [];\n        foreach ($inDegree as $node => $degree) {\n            if ($degree === 0) {\n                $queue[] = $node;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        $result = [];\n        while (!empty($queue)) {\n            sort($queue); // 按字母顺序排序\n            $node = array_shift($queue);\n            $result[] = $node;\n            \n            foreach ($graph[$node] as $neighbor) {\n                $inDegree[$neighbor]--;\n                if ($inDegree[$neighbor] === 0) {\n                    $queue[] = $neighbor;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return $result;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 加载单个插件\n     */\n    protected function loadPlugin(array $plugin): void\n    {\n        $manifest = $plugin['manifest'];\n        $path = $plugin['path'];\n        \n        // 1. 注册自动加载\n        $this->registerAutoload($manifest, $path);\n        \n        // 2. 加载配置\n        $this->loadPluginConfig($manifest, $path);\n        \n        // 3. 注册服务提供者\n        $this->registerProviders($manifest);\n        \n        // 4. 标记为已加载\n        $this->enabledPlugins[$manifest->getName()] = $plugin;\n        \n        $this->logger->info(\"Plugin loaded: {$manifest->getName()} v{$manifest->getVersion()}\");\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 注册插件自动加载\n     */\n    protected function registerAutoload(PluginManifest $manifest, string $path): void\n    {\n        $namespace = $manifest->getNamespace();\n        \n        spl_autoload_register(function (string $class) use ($namespace, $path) {\n            if (!str_starts_with($class, $namespace . '\\\\')) {\n                return false;\n            }\n            \n            $relativeClass = str_replace($namespace . '\\\\', '', $class);\n            $file = $path . '/' . str_replace('\\\\', '/', $relativeClass) . '.php';\n            \n            if (file_exists($file)) {\n                require $file;\n                return true;\n            }\n            \n            return false;\n        });\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 加载插件配置\n     */\n    protected function loadPluginConfig(PluginManifest $manifest, string $path): void\n    {\n        $configFile = BASE_PATH . \"/config/plugin/{$manifest->getName()}.php\";\n        \n        // 运行时配置（用户可修改）\n        $runtimeConfig = [];\n        if (file_exists($configFile)) {\n            $runtimeConfig = require $configFile;\n        }\n        \n        // 合并默认配置\n        $defaultConfig = $manifest->getConfig();\n        $finalConfig = array_merge($defaultConfig, $runtimeConfig);\n        \n        // 注册到容器参数\n        $this->container->setParameter(\"plugin.{$manifest->getName()}\", $finalConfig);\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 注册插件服务提供者\n     */\n    protected function registerProviders(PluginManifest $manifest): void\n    {\n        $providers = $manifest->getProviders();\n        \n        foreach ($providers as $providerClass) {\n            if (!class_exists($providerClass)) {\n                $this->logger->warning(\"Provider not found: {$providerClass}\");\n                continue;\n            }\n            \n            // 通过容器实例化并调用 register\n            $provider = $this->container->make($providerClass);\n            \n            if (method_exists($provider, 'register')) {\n                // 创建 ContainerConfigurator 并调用 register\n                // 这里需要适配到现有的 ServiceProviderInterface\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 安装插件\n     */\n    public function install(string $pluginName): bool\n    {\n        if (!isset($this->plugins[$pluginName])) {\n            throw new PluginException(\"Plugin not found: {$pluginName}\");\n        }\n        \n        $plugin = $this->plugins[$pluginName];\n        $manifest = $plugin['manifest'];\n        \n        // 检查依赖\n        $this->checkDependencies($manifest);\n        \n        // 检查版本兼容性\n        $this->checkVersionCompatibility($manifest);\n        \n        // 执行安装钩子\n        $this->executeHook($manifest, 'install');\n        \n        // 运行数据库迁移\n        $this->runMigrations($plugin['path'], 'up');\n        \n        // 更新配置文件\n        $this->updateInstalledPlugins($pluginName, $manifest->getVersion());\n        \n        // 同步插件配置到 config/plugin/\n        $this->syncPluginConfig($manifest, $plugin['path']);\n        \n        $this->logger->info(\"Plugin installed: {$pluginName}\");\n        return true;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 卸载插件\n     */\n    public function uninstall(string $pluginName): bool\n    {\n        if (!isset($this->config['installed'][$pluginName])) {\n            throw new PluginException(\"Plugin not installed: {$pluginName}\");\n        }\n        \n        // 检查是否有其他插件依赖此插件\n        $dependents = $this->getDependentPlugins($pluginName);\n        if (!empty($dependents)) {\n            throw new PluginException(\n                \"Cannot uninstall: plugins [\" . implode(', ', $dependents) . \"] depend on this plugin\"\n            );\n        }\n        \n        $plugin = $this->plugins[$pluginName];\n        $manifest = $plugin['manifest'];\n        \n        // 先禁用\n        if ($this->config['installed'][$pluginName]['enabled']) {\n            $this->disable($pluginName);\n        }\n        \n        // 执行卸载钩子\n        $this->executeHook($manifest, 'uninstall');\n        \n        // 回滚数据库迁移\n        $this->runMigrations($plugin['path'], 'down');\n        \n        // 从已安装列表移除\n        $this->removeFromInstalledPlugins($pluginName);\n        \n        // 删除配置文件\n        $this->removePluginConfig($pluginName);\n        \n        $this->logger->info(\"Plugin uninstalled: {$pluginName}\");\n        return true;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 启用插件\n     */\n    public function enable(string $pluginName): bool\n    {\n        if (!isset($this->config['installed'][$pluginName])) {\n            throw new PluginException(\"Plugin not installed: {$pluginName}\");\n        }\n        \n        $plugin = $this->plugins[$pluginName];\n        $manifest = $plugin['manifest'];\n        \n        // 检查依赖插件是否已启用\n        $deps = $manifest->getDependencies();\n        foreach ($deps as $dep => $version) {\n            if (!isset($this->config['installed'][$dep]) || \n                !$this->config['installed'][$dep]['enabled']) {\n                throw new PluginException(\"Dependency plugin not enabled: {$dep}\");\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 执行启用钩子\n        $this->executeHook($manifest, 'enable');\n        \n        // 更新状态\n        $this->updatePluginStatus($pluginName, true);\n        \n        // 清除路由缓存\n        $this->clearRouteCache();\n        \n        $this->logger->info(\"Plugin enabled: {$pluginName}\");\n        return true;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 禁用插件\n     */\n    public function disable(string $pluginName): bool\n    {\n        if (!isset($this->config['installed'][$pluginName])) {\n            throw new PluginException(\"Plugin not installed: {$pluginName}\");\n        }\n        \n        // 检查是否有其他启用的插件依赖此插件\n        $dependents = $this->getDependentPlugins($pluginName, true);\n        if (!empty($dependents)) {\n            throw new PluginException(\n                \"Cannot disable: plugins [\" . implode(', ', $dependents) . \"] depend on this plugin\"\n            );\n        }\n        \n        $plugin = $this->plugins[$pluginName];\n        $manifest = $plugin['manifest'];\n        \n        // 执行禁用钩子\n        $this->executeHook($manifest, 'disable');\n        \n        // 更新状态\n        $this->updatePluginStatus($pluginName, false);\n        \n        // 清除路由缓存\n        $this->clearRouteCache();\n        \n        $this->logger->info(\"Plugin disabled: {$pluginName}\");\n        return true;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 获取所有插件的控制器目录\n     */\n    public function getPluginControllerDirs(): array\n    {\n        $dirs = [];\n        \n        foreach ($this->enabledPlugins as $name => $plugin) {\n            $controllerDir = $plugin['path'] . '/Controllers';\n            if (is_dir($controllerDir)) {\n                $dirs[$name] = [\n                    'path' => $controllerDir,\n                    'namespace' => $plugin['manifest']->getNamespace() . '\\\\Controllers',\n                    'route_config' => $plugin['manifest']->getRouteConfig(),\n                ];\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return $dirs;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 执行生命周期钩子\n     */\n    protected function executeHook(PluginManifest $manifest, string $hook): void\n    {\n        $hooks = $manifest->getHooks();\n        \n        if (!isset($hooks[$hook])) {\n            return;\n        }\n        \n        $callback = $hooks[$hook];\n        \n        if (!is_string($callback)) {\n            return;\n        }\n        \n        // 解析类和方法\n        if (str_contains($callback, '::')) {\n            [$class, $method] = explode('::', $callback, 2);\n        } else {\n            $class = $callback;\n            $method = $hook;\n        }\n        \n        if (!class_exists($class)) {\n            $this->logger->warning(\"Hook class not found: {$class}\");\n            return;\n        }\n        \n        $instance = new $class();\n        $instance->{$method}();\n    }\n    \n    // ... 其他辅助方法\n    \n    protected function checkDependencies(PluginManifest $manifest): void { /* ... */ }\n    protected function checkVersionCompatibility(PluginManifest $manifest): void { /* ... */ }\n    protected function runMigrations(string $path, string $direction): void { /* ... */ }\n    protected function updateInstalledPlugins(string $name, string $version): void { /* ... */ }\n    protected function syncPluginConfig(PluginManifest $manifest, string $path): void { /* ... */ }\n    protected function removeFromInstalledPlugins(string $name): void { /* ... */ }\n    protected function removePluginConfig(string $name): void { /* ... */ }\n    protected function updatePluginStatus(string $name, bool $enabled): void { /* ... */ }\n    protected function clearRouteCache(): void { /* ... */ }\n    protected function getDependentPlugins(string $name, bool $onlyEnabled = false): array { /* ... */ }\n}\n```\n\n### 2.5 框架核心重构\n\n#### 2.5.1 修改 AttributeRouteLoader.php（支持多目录扫描）\n\n```php\n<?php\nnamespace Framework\\Core;\n\nuse Symfony\\Component\\Routing\\RouteCollection;\n\nclass AttributeRouteLoader\n{\n    // ... 现有代码保持不变 ...\n    \n    /**\n     * 从多个目录加载路由\n     * \n     * @param array $controllerDirs 控制器目录配置数组\n     *   格式: [\n     *     'app' => ['path' => '/path/to/app/Controllers', 'namespace' => 'App\\Controllers', 'route_config' => []],\n     *     'blog_plugin' => ['path' => '/path/to/plugins/Blog/Controllers', 'namespace' => 'Plugin\\Blog\\Controllers', 'route_config' => ['prefix' => '/blog']]\n     *   ]\n     */\n    public function loadRoutesFromMultipleDirs(array $controllerDirs): RouteCollection\n    {\n        $mainCollection = new RouteCollection();\n        \n        foreach ($controllerDirs as $name => $config) {\n            $collection = $this->loadRoutesFromDir(\n                $config['path'],\n                $config['namespace'],\n                $config['route_config'] ?? []\n            );\n            \n            // 添加集合时带有前缀（如果配置了）\n            if (!empty($config['route_config']['prefix'])) {\n                $mainCollection->addCollection(\n                    $collection, \n                    $config['route_config']['prefix']\n                );\n            } else {\n                $mainCollection->addCollection($collection);\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return $mainCollection;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 从单个目录加载路由\n     */\n    public function loadRoutesFromDir(\n        string $controllerDir, \n        string $namespace,\n        array $routeConfig = []\n    ): RouteCollection {\n        // 临时设置当前目录和命名空间\n        $originalDir = $this->controller_dir;\n        $originalNamespace = $this->controller_namespace;\n        \n        $this->controller_dir = $controllerDir;\n        $this->controller_namespace = $namespace;\n        $this->scanned_files_cache = null; // 清除缓存\n        \n        // 加载路由\n        $collection = $this->loadRoutes();\n        \n        // 应用路由配置\n        if (!empty($routeConfig['middleware'])) {\n            $this->applyMiddlewareToCollection($collection, $routeConfig['middleware']);\n        }\n        \n        // 恢复原始设置\n        $this->controller_dir = $originalDir;\n        $this->controller_namespace = $originalNamespace;\n        $this->scanned_files_cache = null;\n        \n        return $collection;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 为路由集合应用中间件\n     */\n    protected function applyMiddlewareToCollection(RouteCollection $collection, array $middleware): void\n    {\n        foreach ($collection->all() as $route) {\n            $existingMiddleware = $route->getDefault('_middleware') ?? [];\n            $mergedMiddleware = array_unique(array_merge($middleware, (array)$existingMiddleware));\n            $route->setDefault('_middleware', $mergedMiddleware);\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n#### 2.5.2 修改 Framework.php（集成插件系统）\n\n```php\n<?php\nnamespace Framework\\Core;\n\nuse Framework\\Plugin\\PluginManager;\n\nfinal class Framework\n{\n    // 移除硬编码常量，改为配置化\n    // private const CONTROLLER_DIR = BASE_PATH . '/app/Controllers';\n    // private const CONTROLLER_NAMESPACE = 'App\\Controllers';\n    \n    private ?PluginManager $pluginManager = null;\n    \n    /**\n     * 初始化路由和中间件\n     */\n    private function initializeDependencies(): void\n    {\n        // 1. 初始化插件管理器\n        $this->pluginManager = new PluginManager(\n            Container::getInstance(),\n            $this->logger\n        );\n        \n        // 2. 发现插件\n        $this->pluginManager->discover();\n        \n        // 3. 加载已启用的插件\n        $this->pluginManager->loadEnabled();\n        \n        // 4. 加载路由（包含插件路由）\n        $allRoutes = $this->loadAllRoutes();\n        \n        // ... 其余代码保持不变 ...\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 加载所有路由（主应用 + 插件）\n     */\n    private function loadAllRoutes(): RouteCollection\n    {\n        $isProduction = $this->isProduction();\n        \n        // 生产环境缓存检查\n        if ($isProduction && file_exists(self::ROUTE_CACHE_FILE)) {\n            // ... 现有缓存逻辑 ...\n        }\n        \n        $allRoutes = new RouteCollection();\n        \n        // 1. 加载手动路由\n        $this->loadManualRoutes($allRoutes);\n        \n        // 2. 准备控制器目录配置\n        $controllerDirs = $this->getControllerDirectories();\n        \n        // 3. 加载 Attribute 注解路由（主应用 + 插件）\n        $attrLoader = new AttributeRouteLoader(\n            $controllerDirs['app']['path'],\n            $controllerDirs['app']['namespace']\n        );\n        \n        // 加载主应用路由\n        $allRoutes->addCollection($attrLoader->loadRoutes());\n        \n        // 4. 加载插件路由\n        if ($this->pluginManager) {\n            $pluginRoutes = $attrLoader->loadRoutesFromMultipleDirs(\n                $this->pluginManager->getPluginControllerDirs()\n            );\n            $allRoutes->addCollection($pluginRoutes);\n        }\n        \n        // 生产环境缓存\n        if ($isProduction) {\n            $this->cacheRoutes($allRoutes);\n        }\n        \n        return $allRoutes;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 获取控制器目录配置\n     */\n    private function getControllerDirectories(): array\n    {\n        // 主应用目录（可配置化）\n        $controllerDirs = [\n            'app' => [\n                'path' => config('app.controller_dir', BASE_PATH . '/app/Controllers'),\n                'namespace' => config('app.controller_namespace', 'App\\Controllers'),\n                'route_config' => [],\n            ],\n        ];\n        \n        return $controllerDirs;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 获取插件管理器\n     */\n    public function getPluginManager(): ?PluginManager\n    {\n        return $this->pluginManager;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n#### 2.5.3 修改 Router.php（支持多命名空间）\n\n```php\n<?php\nnamespace Framework\\Core;\n\nclass Router\n{\n    // 移除硬编码常量\n    // private const DEFAULT_CONTROLLER_NAMESPACE = 'App\\Controllers';\n    \n    // 改为支持多个命名空间\n    private array $controllerNamespaces = [];\n    \n    public function __construct(\n        RouteCollection $routes,\n        ContainerInterface $container,\n        array $controllerNamespaces = ['App\\\\Controllers']\n    ) {\n        $this->routes = $routes;\n        $this->container = $container;\n        $this->controllerNamespaces = $controllerNamespaces;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 添加控制器命名空间\n     */\n    public function addControllerNamespace(string $namespace): self\n    {\n        if (!in_array($namespace, $this->controllerNamespaces)) {\n            $this->controllerNamespaces[] = $namespace;\n        }\n        return $this;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 构建控制器类名（支持多命名空间）\n     */\n    private function buildControllerClass(array $segments): ?string\n    {\n        $segments = array_map(\n            fn($s) => preg_replace('/[^a-zA-Z0-9_]/', '', $s),\n            $segments\n        );\n\n        if (!$segments) {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        $segments = array_map('ucfirst', $segments);\n        \n        // 遍历所有命名空间\n        foreach ($this->controllerNamespaces as $namespace) {\n            // 尝试1: 完整命名空间类\n            $base = $namespace . '\\\\' . implode('\\\\', $segments);\n            if (class_exists($base)) {\n                return $base;\n            }\n\n            // 尝试2: 带有 Controller 后缀\n            $segmentsCopy = $segments;\n            $segmentsCopy[count($segmentsCopy) - 1] .= 'Controller';\n            $fallback = $namespace . '\\\\' . implode('\\\\', $segmentsCopy);\n\n            if (class_exists($fallback)) {\n                return $fallback;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return null;\n    }\n    \n    // ... 其余代码保持不变 ...\n}\n```\n\n### 2.6 数据库设计\n\n#### 2.6.1 插件表迁移文件\n\n```php\n<?php\n// database/migrations/20240101_create_plugins_table.php\n\nuse think\\migration\\Migrator;\n\nclass CreatePluginsTable extends Migrator\n{\n    public function change()\n    {\n        $table = $this->table('sys_plugins', [\n            'engine' => 'InnoDB',\n            'collation' => 'utf8mb4_unicode_ci',\n            'comment' => '系统插件表'\n        ]);\n        \n        $table->addColumn('name', 'string', [\n                'limit' => 100,\n                'comment' => '插件名称（如 nova/blog）'\n            ])\n            ->addColumn('title', 'string', [\n                'limit' => 200,\n                'comment' => '插件标题'\n            ])\n            ->addColumn('version', 'string', [\n                'limit' => 20,\n                'comment' => '版本号'\n            ])\n            ->addColumn('description', 'text', [\n                'null' => true,\n                'comment' => '插件描述'\n            ])\n            ->addColumn('enabled', 'boolean', [\n                'default' => false,\n                'comment' => '是否启用'\n            ])\n            ->addColumn('installed', 'boolean', [\n                'default' => false,\n                'comment' => '是否已安装'\n            ])\n            ->addColumn('config', 'json', [\n                'null' => true,\n                'comment' => '插件配置JSON'\n            ])\n            ->addColumn('installed_at', 'timestamp', [\n                'null' => true,\n                'comment' => '安装时间'\n            ])\n            ->addColumn('updated_at', 'timestamp', [\n                'null' => true,\n                'comment' => '更新时间'\n            ])\n            ->addIndex(['name'], ['unique' => true])\n            ->create();\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 2.7 插件示例：Blog 插件\n\n#### 2.7.1 目录结构\n\n```\n/plugins/Blog/\n├── plugin.json\n├── Controllers/\n│   └── PostController.php\n├── Services/\n│   └── PostService.php\n├── Models/\n│   ├── Post.php\n│   └── Category.php\n├── Providers/\n│   └── BlogServiceProvider.php\n├── database/\n│   └── migrations/\n│       └── 20240101_create_blog_tables.php\n├── views/\n│   └── post/\n│       └── list.html.twig\n├── Install.php\n└── config.php\n```\n\n#### 2.7.2 PostController.php\n\n```php\n<?php\nnamespace Plugin\\Blog\\Controllers;\n\nuse Framework\\Basic\\BaseController;\nuse Framework\\Basic\\BaseJsonResponse;\nuse Framework\\Attributes\\Route;\nuse Framework\\Attributes\\Auth;\nuse Plugin\\Blog\\Services\\PostService;\nuse Symfony\\Component\\HttpFoundation\\Request;\n\n#[Route(path: '/blog', name: 'blog.')]\nclass PostController extends BaseController\n{\n    protected string $serviceClass = PostService::class;\n    \n    #[Route(path: '/posts', methods: ['GET'], name: 'post.list')]\n    public function list(Request $request): BaseJsonResponse\n    {\n        $page = (int) $this->input('page', 1);\n        $limit = (int) $this->input('limit', 10);\n        \n        $result = $this->service->getList($page, $limit);\n        \n        return $this->success($result);\n    }\n    \n    #[Route(path: '/posts/{id}', methods: ['GET'], name: 'post.detail')]\n    public function detail(Request $request): BaseJsonResponse\n    {\n        $id = (int) $request->attributes->get('id');\n        $post = $this->service->findById($id);\n        \n        if (!$post) {\n            return $this->fail('文章不存在', 404);\n        }\n        \n        return $this->success($post);\n    }\n    \n    #[Route(path: '/posts', methods: ['POST'], name: 'post.create')]\n    #[Auth(required: true, roles: ['admin', 'editor'])]\n    public function create(Request $request): BaseJsonResponse\n    {\n        $data = $this->inputAll();\n        \n        // 验证\n        if (empty($data['title']) || empty($data['content'])) {\n            return $this->fail('标题和内容不能为空');\n        }\n        \n        $post = $this->service->create($data);\n        \n        return $this->success($post, '创建成功');\n    }\n}\n```\n\n#### 2.7.3 BlogServiceProvider.php\n\n```php\n<?php\nnamespace Plugin\\Blog\\Providers;\n\nuse Framework\\Container\\ServiceProviderInterface;\nuse Symfony\\Component\\DependencyInjection\\ContainerInterface;\nuse Symfony\\Component\\DependencyInjection\\Loader\\Configurator\\ContainerConfigurator;\nuse Plugin\\Blog\\Services\\PostService;\n\nclass BlogServiceProvider implements ServiceProviderInterface\n{\n    public function register(ContainerConfigurator $configurator): void\n    {\n        $services = $configurator->services();\n        \n        // 注册 PostService\n        $services->set(PostService::class)\n            ->autowire()\n            ->autoconfigure()\n            ->public();\n    }\n    \n    public function boot(ContainerInterface $container): void\n    {\n        // 启动时执行的逻辑，如注册事件监听器等\n    }\n}\n```\n\n#### 2.7.4 Install.php\n\n```php\n<?php\nnamespace Plugin\\Blog;\n\nclass Install\n{\n    /**\n     * 安装时执行\n     */\n    public static function run(): void\n    {\n        echo \"Installing Blog plugin...\\n\";\n        // 可以执行其他初始化操作\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 卸载时执行\n     */\n    public static function uninstall(): void\n    {\n        echo \"Uninstalling Blog plugin...\\n\";\n        // 清理数据等\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 启用时执行\n     */\n    public static function enable(): void\n    {\n        echo \"Enabling Blog plugin...\\n\";\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 禁用时执行\n     */\n    public static function disable(): void\n    {\n        echo \"Disabling Blog plugin...\\n\";\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * 升级时执行\n     */\n    public static function upgrade(string $oldVersion, string $newVersion): void\n    {\n        echo \"Upgrading Blog plugin from {$oldVersion} to {$newVersion}...\\n\";\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、重构步骤与优先级\n\n### 3.1 第一阶段：基础架构（优先级：高）\n\n1. **创建插件核心目录和接口**\n   - 创建 `/framework/Plugin/` 目录\n   - 实现 `PluginInterface.php`\n   - 实现 `PluginManifest.php`\n   - 实现 `PluginException.php`\n\n2. **实现插件配置机制**\n   - 创建 `/config/plugin/` 目录\n   - 创建 `plugins.php` 配置文件模板\n\n3. **修改框架常量为配置化**\n   - 修改 `Framework.php`，移除硬编码常量\n   - 将控制器目录和命名空间改为从配置读取\n\n### 3.2 第二阶段：核心功能（优先级：高）\n\n1. **实现 PluginManager 核心逻辑**\n   - 插件发现（`discover()`）\n   - 插件加载（`loadEnabled()`）\n   - 依赖解析（拓扑排序）\n\n2. **重构 AttributeRouteLoader**\n   - 添加 `loadRoutesFromMultipleDirs()` 方法\n   - 支持路由前缀和中间件配置\n\n3. **重构 Router**\n   - 支持多命名空间控制器解析\n\n### 3.3 第三阶段：生命周期管理（优先级：中）\n\n1. **实现插件生命周期方法**\n   - `install()` - 安装\n   - `uninstall()` - 卸载\n   - `enable()` - 启用\n   - `disable()` - 禁用\n\n2. **数据库迁移支持**\n   - 创建插件数据库表\n   - 实现插件迁移文件执行器\n\n3. **配置同步机制**\n   - 插件配置文件的创建与同步\n\n### 3.4 第四阶段：CLI 工具（优先级：中）\n\n1. **创建命令行工具**\n   - `plugin:install` - 安装插件\n   - `plugin:uninstall` - 卸载插件\n   - `plugin:enable` - 启用插件\n   - `plugin:disable` - 禁用插件\n   - `plugin:list` - 列出插件\n   - `plugin:migrate` - 运行插件迁移\n\n### 3.5 第五阶段：高级功能（优先级：低）\n\n1. **版本升级机制**\n2. **插件市场集成**\n3. **插件权限系统**\n4. **插件钩子（Hook）系统**\n\n---\n\n## 四、向后兼容性保证\n\n### 4.1 现有代码无需修改\n\n- 主应用控制器继续使用 `App\\Controllers` 命名空间\n- 现有路由注解 `#[Route]` 继续有效\n- 现有服务提供者机制保持不变\n\n### 4.2 渐进式迁移\n\n```php\n// 旧代码（继续支持）\n// Framework.php\nprivate const CONTROLLER_DIR = BASE_PATH . '/app/Controllers';\n\n// 新代码（推荐）\n// config/app.php\nreturn [\n    'controller_dir' => env('APP_CONTROLLER_DIR', BASE_PATH . '/app/Controllers'),\n    'controller_namespace' => env('APP_CONTROLLER_NAMESPACE', 'App\\Controllers'),\n];\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、关键文件清单\n\n| 文件路径 | 操作 | 说明 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| `/framework/Plugin/PluginInterface.php` | 新增 | 插件接口定义 |\n| `/framework/Plugin/PluginManifest.php` | 新增 | 插件清单解析 |\n| `/framework/Plugin/PluginManager.php` | 新增 | 插件管理器核心 |\n| `/framework/Plugin/PluginException.php` | 新增 | 插件异常类 |\n| `/framework/Core/AttributeRouteLoader.php` | 修改 | 支持多目录扫描 |\n| `/framework/Core/Framework.php` | 修改 | 集成插件系统 |\n| `/framework/Core/Router.php` | 修改 | 支持多命名空间 |\n| `/config/plugin/plugins.php` | 新增 | 插件配置清单 |\n| `/database/migrations/*_create_plugins_table.php` | 新增 | 插件数据库表 |\n\n---\n\n## 六、总结\n\n本设计方案基于 NovaFrame PHP 框架现有架构，设计了一套完整的插件系统，核心特点包括：\n\n1. **多应用模式**：插件被视为主应用的扩展，每个插件有独立的命名空间和目录结构\n2. **依赖管理**：支持插件间依赖关系，使用拓扑排序确保正确的加载顺序\n3. **生命周期管理**：完整的安装、卸载、启用、禁用、升级流程\n4. **配置隔离**：每个插件有独立的配置文件，用户可覆盖默认配置\n5. **路由扩展**：支持插件独立路由，可配置前缀和中间件\n6. **向后兼容**：现有主应用代码无需修改，渐进式迁移\n"},"tool_response":"Successfully overwrote file: /root/.codebuddy/plans/blazing-forging-turing.md","client":"CLI","version":"2.66.2","generation_id":"047663c9d19246c096d5f66b0a4e5c5c","model":"glm-5.0"}
