[2026-03-31 03:07:48] [DEBUG] [PPT PostToolUse Hook] stdin 数据: {"session_id":"2038809571990573056","transcript_path":"/root/.codebuddy/projects/workspace/2038809571990573056.jsonl","cwd":"/workspace","hook_event_name":"PostToolUse","tool_name":"Write","tool_input":{"file_path":"/root/.codebuddy/plans/blazing-forging-turing.md","content":"# NovaFrame PHP 框架插件系统设计方案\n\n## 一、框架现状分析\n\n### 1.1 核心架构\n\n| 组件 | 技术方案 | 文件路径 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| 服务容器 | Symfony DI Container | `framework/Container/Container.php` |\n| 服务提供者 | ServiceProviderInterface | `framework/Container/ServiceProviderInterface.php` |\n| 路由系统 | Symfony Routing + PHP 8 Attributes | `framework/Core/Router.php` |\n| 路由加载 | AttributeRouteLoader | `framework/Core/AttributeRouteLoader.php` |\n| 框架入口 | Framework 单例 | `framework/Core/Framework.php` |\n| 控制器基类 | BaseController | `framework/Basic/BaseController.php` |\n\n### 1.2 关键问题\n\n**硬编码问题** - 需要重构：\n\n```php\n// framework/Core/Framework.php (第40-42行)\nprivate const CONTROLLER_DIR = BASE_PATH . '/app/Controllers';\nprivate const CONTROLLER_NAMESPACE = 'App\\Controllers';\n```\n\n```php\n// framework/Core/AttributeRouteLoader.php (构造函数)\npublic function __construct(string $controller_dir, string $controller_namespace, ...)\n```\n\n路由加载器只支持单一目录和命名空间，无法扩展到插件。\n\n### 1.3 现有优势\n\n- ✅ Symfony DI 容器支持服务提供者模式\n- ✅ PHP 8 Attributes 注解路由，易于扩展\n- ✅ 中间件系统完善\n- ✅ 事件监听器支持注解注册\n\n---\n\n## 二、插件系统设计\n\n### 2.1 目录结构\n\n```\n/workspace\n├── app/                          # 主应用（保持不变）\n│   ├── Controllers/\n│   ├── Models/\n│   ├── Services/\n│   └── Providers/\n├── plugins/                      # 插件根目录（新增）\n│   ├── blog/                     # 示例：博客插件\n│   │   ├── Controllers/\n│   │   │   └── PostController.php\n│   │   ├── Models/\n│   │   │   └── Post.php\n│   │   ├── Services/\n│   │   │   └── PostService.php\n│   │   ├── Providers/\n│   │   │   └── BlogServiceProvider.php\n│   │   ├── database/\n│   │   │   ├── migrations/\n│   │   │   └── seeds/\n│   │   ├── routes.php            # 可选：手动路由定义\n│   │   └── plugin.json           # 插件元数据\n│   └── payment/                  # 示例：支付插件\n│       └── ...\n├── config/\n│   ├── plugin/                   # 插件配置目录（新增）\n│   │   ├── plugins.php           # 已安装插件清单\n│   │   ├── blog.php              # 博客插件运行时配置\n│   │   └── payment.php           # 支付插件运行时配置\n│   └── ...\n└── framework/\n    └── Plugin/                   # 插件核心组件（新增）\n        ├── PluginInterface.php\n        ├── PluginManifest.php\n        ├── PluginManager.php\n        └── PluginServiceProvider.php\n```\n\n### 2.2 插件元数据规范\n\n**`plugins/blog/plugin.json`**：\n\n```json\n{\n    \"name\": \"blog\",\n    \"title\": \"博客管理\",\n    \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n    \"description\": \"博客文章管理插件\",\n    \"author\": \"NovaFrame Team\",\n    \"namespace\": \"Plugins\\\\Blog\",\n    \"requires\": {\n        \"php\": \"^8.3\",\n        \"novaframe\": \"^0.8.0\"\n    },\n    \"dependencies\": {\n        \"payment\": \"^1.0.0\"\n    },\n    \"autoload\": {\n        \"psr-4\": {\n            \"Plugins\\\\Blog\\\\\": \"\"\n        }\n    },\n    \"hooks\": {\n        \"install\": \"Plugins\\\\Blog\\\\InstallHook\",\n        \"uninstall\": \"Plugins\\\\Blog\\\\UninstallHook\",\n        \"enable\": \"Plugins\\\\Blog\\\\EnableHook\",\n        \"disable\": \"Plugins\\\\Blog\\\\DisableHook\"\n    },\n    \"routes\": {\n        \"prefix\": \"/blog\",\n        \"middleware\": [\"auth\"]\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 2.3 插件清单配置\n\n**`config/plugin/plugins.php`**：\n\n```php\n<?php\nreturn [\n    // 已安装插件列表\n    'installed' => [\n        'blog' => [\n            'enabled' => true,\n            'version' => '1.0.0',\n            'installed_at' => '2025-01-15 10:30:00',\n        ],\n        'payment' => [\n            'enabled' => true,\n            'version' => '1.2.0',\n            'installed_at' => '2025-01-10 14:20:00',\n        ],\n    ],\n    \n    // 插件扫描目录\n    'paths' => [\n        BASE_PATH . '/plugins',\n    ],\n];\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、核心组件实现\n\n### 3.1 插件接口\n\n**`framework/Plugin/PluginInterface.php`**：\n\n```php\n<?php\nnamespace Framework\\Plugin;\n\ninterface PluginInterface\n{\n    /**\n     * 获取插件名称\n     */\n    public function getName(): string;\n\n    /**\n     * 获取插件版本\n     */\n    public function getVersion(): string;\n\n    /**\n     * 插件安装时调用\n     */\n    public function install(): void;\n\n    /**\n     * 插件卸载时调用\n     */\n    public function uninstall(): void;\n\n    /**\n     * 插件启用时调用\n     */\n    public function enable(): void;\n\n    /**\n     * 插件禁用时调用\n     */\n    public function disable(): void;\n}\n```\n\n### 3.2 插件清单解析器\n\n**`framework/Plugin/PluginManifest.php`**：\n\n```php\n<?php\nnamespace Framework\\Plugin;\n\nclass PluginManifest\n{\n    public function __construct(\n        public readonly string $name,\n        public readonly string $title,\n        public readonly string $version,\n        public readonly string $namespace,\n        public readonly string $path,\n        public readonly array $requires = [],\n        public readonly array $dependencies = [],\n        public readonly array $hooks = [],\n        public readonly array $routes = [],\n    ) {}\n\n    /**\n     * 从 plugin.json 文件解析\n     */\n    public static function fromFile(string $jsonPath): self\n    {\n        $json = file_get_contents($jsonPath);\n        $data = json_decode($json, true, 512, JSON_THROW_ON_ERROR);\n        \n        return new self(\n            name: $data['name'],\n            title: $data['title'] ?? $data['name'],\n            version: $data['version'],\n            namespace: $data['namespace'] ?? \"Plugins\\\\{$data['name']}\",\n            path: dirname($jsonPath),\n            requires: $data['requires'] ?? [],\n            dependencies: $data['dependencies'] ?? [],\n            hooks: $data['hooks'] ?? [],\n            routes: $data['routes'] ?? [],\n        );\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 3.3 插件管理器\n\n**`framework/Plugin/PluginManager.php`**：\n\n```php\n<?php\nnamespace Framework\\Plugin;\n\nuse Framework\\Container\\Container;\nuse InvalidArgumentException;\n\nclass PluginManager\n{\n    private array $plugins = [];\n    private array $manifests = [];\n    private array $config;\n\n    public function __construct(array $config = [])\n    {\n        $this->config = $config;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * 发现所有插件\n     */\n    public function discover(): void\n    {\n        $paths = $this->config['paths'] ?? [BASE_PATH . '/plugins'];\n        \n        foreach ($paths as $path) {\n            if (!is_dir($path)) {\n                continue;\n            }\n            \n            foreach (scandir($path) as $dir) {\n                if ($dir === '.' || $dir === '..') {\n                    continue;\n                }\n                \n                $manifestPath = \"{$path}/{$dir}/plugin.json\";\n                if (file_exists($manifestPath)) {\n                    $manifest = PluginManifest::fromFile($manifestPath);\n                    $this->manifests[$manifest->name] = $manifest;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * 加载已启用的插件\n     */\n    public function loadEnabled(): void\n    {\n        $installed = $this->config['installed'] ?? [];\n        \n        // 拓扑排序确保依赖顺序\n        $sortedPlugins = $this->sortByDependencies($installed);\n        \n        foreach ($sortedPlugins as $name => $info) {\n            if (!($info['enabled'] ?? false)) {\n                continue;\n            }\n            \n            if (!isset($this->manifests[$name])) {\n                continue;\n            }\n            \n            $this->load($name);\n        }\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * 加载单个插件\n     */\n    public function load(string $name): void\n    {\n        $manifest = $this->manifests[$name] ?? null;\n        if (!$manifest) {\n            throw new InvalidArgumentException(\"Plugin not found: {$name}\");\n        }\n\n        // 注册命名空间到 Composer 自动加载\n        $this->registerAutoload($manifest);\n        \n        $this->plugins[$name] = $manifest;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * 获取所有已加载插件的控制器目录\n     */\n    public function getControllerDirs(): array\n    {\n        $dirs = [];\n        foreach ($this->plugins as $manifest) {\n            $controllerDir = \"{$manifest->path}/Controllers\";\n            if (is_dir($controllerDir)) {\n                $dirs[$manifest->namespace . '\\\\Controllers'] = $controllerDir;\n            }\n        }\n        return $dirs;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * 安装插件\n     */\n    public function install(string $name): bool\n    {\n        // 实现安装逻辑\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * 卸载插件\n     */\n    public function uninstall(string $name): bool\n    {\n        // 实现卸载逻辑\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * 启用插件\n     */\n    public function enable(string $name): bool\n    {\n        // 实现启用逻辑\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * 禁用插件\n     */\n    public function disable(string $name): bool\n    {\n        // 实现禁用逻辑\n    }\n\n    private function registerAutoload(PluginManifest $manifest): void\n    {\n        $loader = require BASE_PATH . '/vendor/autoload.php';\n        $loader->addPsr4($manifest->namespace . '\\\\', $manifest->path);\n    }\n\n    private function sortByDependencies(array $plugins): array\n    {\n        // 拓扑排序实现\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、框架重构方案\n\n### 4.1 修改 AttributeRouteLoader（支持多目录）\n\n**文件**: `framework/Core/AttributeRouteLoader.php`\n\n**修改内容**：\n\n```php\n/**\n * 新增方法：从多个目录加载路由\n */\npublic function loadRoutesFromMultipleDirs(array $controllerDirs): RouteCollection\n{\n    $routeCollection = new RouteCollection();\n    \n    foreach ($controllerDirs as $namespace => $dir) {\n        $routes = $this->loadRoutesFromDir($dir, $namespace);\n        $routeCollection->addCollection($routes);\n    }\n    \n    return $routeCollection;\n}\n\n/**\n * 从单个目录加载路由\n */\nprivate function loadRoutesFromDir(string $controllerDir, string $namespace): RouteCollection\n{\n    // 复用现有的扫描逻辑，但使用传入的 namespace\n    $this->controller_dir = $controllerDir;\n    $this->controller_namespace = $namespace;\n    return $this->loadRoutes();\n}\n```\n\n### 4.2 修改 Framework.php（集成插件管理）\n\n**文件**: `framework/Core/Framework.php`\n\n**修改内容**：\n\n```php\n// 移除硬编码常量，改为配置化\n// private const CONTROLLER_DIR = BASE_PATH . '/app/Controllers';  // 删除\n// private const CONTROLLER_NAMESPACE = 'App\\Controllers';          // 删除\n\nprivate PluginManager $pluginManager;\n\nprivate function initializeDependencies(): void\n{\n    // 1. 初始化插件管理器\n    $pluginConfig = require BASE_PATH . '/config/plugin/plugins.php';\n    $this->pluginManager = new PluginManager($pluginConfig);\n    $this->pluginManager->discover();\n    $this->pluginManager->loadEnabled();\n    \n    // 2. 加载路由（主应用 + 插件）\n    $allRoutes = $this->loadAllRoutes();\n    \n    // ... 其余代码\n}\n\nprivate function loadAllRoutes(): RouteCollection\n{\n    $allRoutes = new RouteCollection();\n    \n    // 1. 加载主应用路由\n    $mainRoutes = $this->loadMainAppRoutes();\n    $allRoutes->addCollection($mainRoutes);\n    \n    // 2. 加载插件路由\n    $pluginRoutes = $this->loadPluginRoutes();\n    $allRoutes->addCollection($pluginRoutes);\n    \n    return $allRoutes;\n}\n\nprivate function loadPluginRoutes(): RouteCollection\n{\n    $pluginRoutes = new RouteCollection();\n    \n    foreach ($this->pluginManager->getControllerDirs() as $namespace => $dir) {\n        $loader = new AttributeRouteLoader($dir, $namespace);\n        $routes = $loader->loadRoutes();\n        $pluginRoutes->addCollection($routes);\n    }\n    \n    return $pluginRoutes;\n}\n```\n\n### 4.3 修改 composer.json（插件命名空间）\n\n**文件**: `composer.json`\n\n```json\n{\n    \"autoload\": {\n        \"psr-4\": {\n            \"Framework\\\\\": \"framework/\",\n            \"App\\\\\": \"app/\",\n            \"Plugins\\\\\": \"plugins/\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、插件生命周期管理\n\n### 5.1 安装流程\n\n```\n1. 上传插件到 /plugins/{name}/\n2. 解析 plugin.json\n3. 检查依赖是否满足\n4. 执行安装钩子（创建数据库表、初始化配置）\n5. 注册到 config/plugin/plugins.php\n6. 清除缓存\n```\n\n### 5.2 卸载流程\n\n```\n1. 检查是否有其他插件